	<features>
		<feature>Traverse an intricate narrative, shaped by ripples of overlapping choice and consequence.</feature>
		<feature>Solve puzzles by manipulating the environment, interpreting signs, and violating causality.</feature>
		<feature>Haunting original score, composed and performed by VANCORVID</feature>
		<feature>Play at your speed. Every choice is reversible.</feature>
		<feature>Ensure that all will happen as it must.</feature>
